I don't care. Lois. If she
wasn't invited to a party...

08:43.977 --> 08:46.144
Lois?
Well, Lois hated parties.

08:46.179 --> 08:47.529
All right, forget Lois. Ruth.

08:47.564 --> 08:48.814
If she wasn't invited
to a party...

08:48.848 --> 08:50.365
Ruth? Well, Ruth...
I didn't know she drank

08:50.400 --> 08:52.501
until I saw her sober.

08:54.170 --> 08:57.639
Let's just forget about
your wives for a minute.

08:57.674 --> 08:59.975
I might have insulted
one of Vanessa's friends,

08:59.993 --> 09:01.577
and now they're not
friends anymore,

09:01.611 --> 09:03.178
and Vanessa's
really worried that

09:03.213 --> 09:05.247
we're not gonna have any friends
and we're gonna end up alone,

09:05.281 --> 09:06.248
even though she's friends...

09:06.282 --> 09:08.016
