in Denver.

09:08.051 --> 09:10.652
Mm. Mike, how many pairs
of shoes do you own?

09:10.687 --> 09:12.754
Uh, uh,
probably five or six,

09:12.789 --> 09:14.189
including the ones
I got on.

09:14.224 --> 09:15.190
And Vanessa?

09:15.225 --> 09:18.710
7 million.
What's the point?

09:18.761 --> 09:20.929
Well, yeah, see, women collect
friends like they collect shoes,

09:20.964 --> 09:22.598
and like shoes,
they never get rid of them,

09:22.632 --> 09:24.600
even if... even if the shoes
are going out of style.

09:24.634 --> 09:26.602
See, women are terrified that
the day they throw them away,

09:26.669 --> 09:28.437
that's the day
that they'll...

09:28.471 --> 09:30.072
that they'll desperately
need them.

09:30.106 --> 09:34.726
See, it's... it's...
