used to say to me,

09:46.322 --> 09:47.289
"a man shouldn't have
more friends

09:47.323 --> 09:49.124
than he can name
in ten seconds."

09:49.158 --> 09:51.126
I like that,
but your dad also said,

09:51.160 --> 09:53.762
"don't date a woman
over 5'2"."

09:53.796 --> 09:57.198
Well, he was a short and lonely man.

