13:03.152 --> 13:04.986
Wh...

13:05.021 --> 13:07.405
Never mind. Never mind.

13:07.440 --> 13:09.391
- He's kinda hot.
- Yeah.

13:09.425 --> 13:11.293
I would totally go for him
if I didn't have a boyfriend

13:11.327 --> 13:13.662
and a baby from another man.

13:13.696 --> 13:16.114
Again,
kudos on the sex talk.

13:16.165 --> 13:18.066
Right.

13:20.970 --> 13:23.705
Mm. We might need something
stronger to get that dent out.

13:23.739 --> 13:24.940
This is
the most effective device

13:24.974 --> 13:27.108
